UR INKS</strong></p> <p style="font-family:trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">  We print with the renowned Epson Ultrachrome K3 Pigment Inks onto quality paper stocks,   ensuring superior image quality, longer print life, deeper colours and greater water and scratch resistance.</p> <p style="font-family:trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">Please click the drop down box at the top of the page to select the size &amp; paper required.</p> <p style="font-family:trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">The picture shown is of reduced quality to enable our eBay listing to load quickly. The quality of the final print will be much higher.   The colour may also vary from the image shown because of different screen settings</p> <p align="center" style="font-family:trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>PACKAGING</strong></p> <p style="font-family:trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">We carefully hand-package in a postal tube to ensure that your item(s) arrive in perfect condition.</p> <p align="center" style="font-family:trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>PAYMENT</strong></p> <p style="font-family:trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">Our preferred payment method is PayPal however we can also accept most other payment methods.</p> <p align="center" style="font-family:trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>RETURNS</strong></p> <p style="font-family:trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;">If for any reason you are unhappy with your product we offer a full money back guarantee on all items   returned to us, we would ask that you contact us within 14 days if you have any problems as we would   prefer to resolve any problems before any feedback is left. </p> <p style="font-family:trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif;font-style: italic;">Please note that although every care is taken to restore &amp; reproduce these posters, quality is limited to the original source. They were   advertising posters, not fine art. Under close scrutiny, some imperfections may be noticeable (as di